00:00:14.550 --> 00:00:16.950
Now the first rule is,

00:00:16.950 --> 00:00:22.754
if the fonts belong to a very big family or a same designer,

00:00:22.754 --> 00:00:26.220
then they will fit together very well.

00:00:26.220 --> 00:00:28.230
Now, why is that?

00:00:28.230 --> 00:00:35.985
Because same designer or same family means mostly the similar geometry.

00:00:35.985 --> 00:00:38.130
So the shapes and angles,

00:00:38.130 --> 00:00:41.160
most of them they will share their traits.

00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:47.150
