00:01:22.935 --> 00:01:26.870
So same family could be a very large family or it

00:01:26.870 --> 00:01:31.250
could be a mix-up of sans-serif or serif of the same type.

00:01:31.250 --> 00:01:36.395
Droid Sans, you might know the Droid Sans and Droid Serif.

00:01:36.395 --> 00:01:41.075
It is also two couple of families and they are basically the same.

00:01:41.075 --> 00:01:45.725
